---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Dario Mory";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <div class="raccoon-frame">
            <img
                width="800"
                height="450"
                alt="Illustration of a raccoon coding at a desk with monitors at night"
                src="/raccoon-coder.webp"
                loading="eager"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
    <h1>Dario Mory</h1>
    <small>Engineering Leader</small> 
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        I build and lead engineering teams that ship AI-powered products-from prototype to production. Past work includes KLM's airport operations stack, the Single Digital Gateway programme for Dutch and EU public services, and startups across Europe and the US.
    </p>
    <p>
        Code that ships, teams that grow-that's what matters. Cloud migrations, high-traffic APIs, and early-stage products taken to production are the kinds of problems that keep things interesting.
    </p>
    <p>
        I speak at conferences on AI engineering and software leadership. Organizing an event? Get in touch.
    </p>
</Layout>
<style>
    /* small */
    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #fdebf3;
        font: 600 14px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #1e1e2e;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }
</style>
